@startuml
skinparam handwritten false
skinparam monochrome true
skinparam class {
    BackgroundColor White
    ArrowColor Black
    BorderColor Black
}

class TickCompletableFuture<T> {
  == Chaining & Callbacks ==
  + thenApply(Function<T, U> fn)
  + thenCompose(Function<T, TickCompletableFuture<U>> fn)
  + whenComplete(BiConsumer<T, Throwable> callback)
  == Resolution ==
  + complete(T result)
  + fail(Throwable exception)
  == State Checking ==
  + isPending() : boolean
  + isCompleted() : boolean
  + isFailed() : boolean
}

note right of TickCompletableFuture::thenApply
  Transforms the result without blocking, 
  returning a new future.
end note

note right of TickCompletableFuture::thenCompose
  Chains another asynchronous operation, 
  flattening nested futures.
end note

note right of TickCompletableFuture::whenComplete
  Registers a callback to handle both 
  success and failure cases sequentially.
end note

note left of TickCompletableFuture::complete
  Deterministically resolves the future
  and triggers callbacks on the same thread.
end note

note left of TickCompletableFuture::fail
  Deterministically fails the future
  and triggers callbacks on the same thread.
end note

note bottom of TickCompletableFuture
  **Core Guarantee:** Callbacks execute synchronously 
  within the tick loop when complete() or fail() is called.
end note

@enduml
